402  inline float getManhattanDistanceTo(float inX, float inY)
403  {
404  if (leftX < inX && inX <= rightX && bottomY < inY && inY <= topY)
405  {
406  return 0;
407  }
408  if (leftX < inX && inX <= rightX)
409  {
410  return std::min(std::fabs(inY - topY), std::fabs(inY - bottomY));
411  }
412  if (bottomY < inY && inY <= topY)
413  {
414  return std::min(std::fabs(inX - leftX), std::fabs(inX - rightX));
415  }
416  return std::min(std::fabs(inX - leftX), std::fabs(inX - rightX)) +
417  std::min(std::fabs(inY - topY), std::fabs(inY - bottomY));
418  }

1091  inline void setSpreadLocation_WithLimitDisplacement(float x, float y, float forgetRatio,
1092  float limitDisplacement)
1093  {
1094  assert(!locked);
1095 
1096  if (lastSpreadX > -100 && lastSpreadY > -100)
1097  {
1098  assert(forgetRatio <= 1);
1099  float disX = std::fabs(x - lastSpreadX) * forgetRatio;
1100  float disY = std::fabs(x - lastSpreadX) * forgetRatio;
1101  float dis = std::sqrt(disX * disX + disY * disY);
1102  if (dis / limitDisplacement > 1)
1103  forgetRatio /= (dis / limitDisplacement);
1104 
1105  x = x * forgetRatio + lastSpreadX * (1 - forgetRatio);
1106  y = y * forgetRatio + lastSpreadY * (1 - forgetRatio);

1865  class PlacementNet
1866  {
1867  public:
1875  PlacementNet(DesignInfo::DesignNet *designNet, int id, std::vector<PlacementUnit *> &cellId2PlacementUnitVec,
1876  PlacementInfo *placementInfo)
1877  : designNet(designNet), id(id), placementInfo(placementInfo)
1878  {
1879  unitsOfNetPins.clear();
1880  unitsOfDriverPins.clear();
1881  unitsOfPinsBeDriven.clear();
1882  PUSet.clear();
1883  for (DesignInfo::DesignPin *curPin : designNet->getPins())
1884  {
1885  PlacementUnit *tmpPU = cellId2PlacementUnitVec[curPin->getCell()->getElementIdInType()];
1886  unitsOfNetPins.push_back(tmpPU);
1887  PUSet.insert(tmpPU);
1888 
1889  if (curPin->isOutputPort())
1890  {
1891  unitsOfDriverPins.push_back(tmpPU);
1892  }
1893  else
1894  {
1895  unitsOfPinsBeDriven.push_back(tmpPU);
1896  }
1897 
1898  if (tmpPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_UnpackedCell)
1899  {
1900  pinOffset tmpPinOffset = pinOffset(curPin->getOffsetXInCell(), curPin->getOffsetYInCell());
1901  pinOffsetsInUnit.push_back(tmpPinOffset);
1902  }
1903  else if (tmpPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_Macro)
1904  {
1905  PlacementMacro *tmpM = dynamic_cast<PlacementMacro *>(tmpPU);
1906  assert(tmpM);
1907  pinOffset tmpPinOffset =
1908  pinOffset(curPin->getOffsetXInCell() + tmpM->getCellOffsetXInMacro(curPin->getCell()),
1909  curPin->getOffsetYInCell() + tmpM->getCellOffsetYInMacro(curPin->getCell()));
1910  pinOffsetsInUnit.push_back(tmpPinOffset);
1911  }
1912  }
1913  leftPuId = rightPuId = topPuId = bottomPuId = -1;
1914  }
1915  ~PlacementNet()
1916  {
1917  }

1995  inline bool updateNetBounds(bool updateX, bool updateY)
1996  {
1997  if (updateX)
1998  {
1999  leftPUX = 1e5;
2000  rightPUX = -1e5;
2001  leftPinX = 1e5;
2002  rightPinX = -1e5;
2003  for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2004  {
2005  auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2006  auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2007  auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2008  float cellX = tmpPU->X();
2009  float pinX = tmpPU->X() + tmpPinOffset.x;
2010  if (pinX < leftPinX)
2011  {
2012  leftPinX = pinX;
2013  leftPUX = cellX;
2014  leftPuId = tmpPUId;
2015  leftPinId_net = pinId_net;
2016  }
2017  if (pinX > rightPinX)
2018  {
2019  rightPinX = pinX;
2020  rightPUX = cellX;
2021  rightPuId = tmpPUId;
2022  rightPinId_net = pinId_net;
2023  }
2024  }
2025  }
2026  if (updateY)
2027  {
2028  topPUY = -1e5;
2029  bottomPUY = 1e5;
2030  topPinY = -1e5;
2031  bottomPinY = 1e5;
2032  for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2033  {
2034  auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2035  auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2036  auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2037  float cellY = tmpPU->Y();
2038  float pinY = tmpPU->Y() + tmpPinOffset.y;
2039  if (pinY < bottomPinY)
2040  {
2041  bottomPinY = pinY;
2042  bottomPUY = cellY;
2043  bottomPuId = tmpPUId;
2044  bottomPinId_net = pinId_net;
2045  }
2046  if (pinY > topPinY)
2047  {
2048  topPinY = pinY;
2049  topPUY = cellY;
2050  topPuId = tmpPUId;
2051  topPinId_net = pinId_net;
2052  }
2053  }
2054  }
2055  return (updateX && (leftPuId != rightPuId)) || (updateY && (topPuId != bottomPuId));
2056  }

2065  inline float getHPWL(float y2xRatio)

2082  inline float getNewHPWLByTrying(PlacementUnit *curPU, double targetPUX, double targetPUY, float y2xRatio) const
2083  {
2084  float tmp_leftX = 1e5;
2085  float tmp_rightX = -1e5;
2086  float tmp_topY = -1e5;
2087  float tmp_bottomY = 1e5;
2088 
2089  for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2090  {
2091  auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2092  auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2093  float pinX;
2094  if (tmpPU == curPU)
2095  {
2096  pinX = targetPUX + tmpPinOffset.x;
2097  }
2098  else
2099  {
2100  pinX = tmpPU->X() + tmpPinOffset.x;
2101  }
2102  if (pinX < tmp_leftX)
2103  {
2104  tmp_leftX = pinX;
2105  }
2106  if (pinX > tmp_rightX)
2107  {
2108  tmp_rightX = pinX;
2109  }
2110  }
2111  for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2112  {
2113  auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2114  auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2115  float pinY;
2116  if (tmpPU == curPU)
2117  {
2118  pinY = targetPUY + tmpPinOffset.y;
2119  }
2120  else
2121  {
2122  pinY = tmpPU->Y() + tmpPinOffset.y;
2123  }
2124  if (pinY < tmp_bottomY)
2125  {
2126  tmp_bottomY = pinY;
2127  }
2128  if (pinY > tmp_topY)
2129  {
2130  tmp_topY = pinY;
2131  }
2132  }
2133 
2134  int A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX;
2135  placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_rightX, tmp_bottomY, A_ClockRegionX,
2136  A_ClockRegionY);
2137  std::pair<int, int> A_ClockLocYX(A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX);
2138 
2139  int B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX;
2140  placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_leftX, tmp_topY, B_cellClockRegionX,
2141  B_cellClockRegionY);
2142  std::pair<int, int> B_ClockLocYX(B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX);
2143 
2144  float clockRegionOverhead = 0;
2145  // if (B_ClockLocYX != A_ClockLocYX)
2146  // {
2147  // clockRegionOverhead = std::abs(B_cellClockRegionX - A_ClockRegionX) * 15;
2148  // }
2149 
2150  return std::fabs(tmp_rightX - tmp_leftX) + y2xRatio * std::fabs(tmp_topY - tmp_bottomY) +
2151  clockRegionOverhead;
2152  }

2173  inline void updateBound2BoundNetWeight(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2174  std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag,
2175  Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, float generalWeight, float y2xRatio,
2176  bool updateX, bool updateY, bool checkClockRegion = false)
2177  {
2178  assert(updateX ^ updateY);
2179  if (pinOffsetsInUnit.size() <= 1)
2180  return;
2181  float w = 2.0 * generalWeight / (float)(pinOffsetsInUnit.size() - 1);
2182  int nPins = pinOffsetsInUnit.size();
2183 
2184  // adopt netDegree Weight from RippeFPGA
2185  if (nPins < 10)
2186  w *= 1.00;
2187  else if (nPins < 20)
2188  w *= 1.2;
2189  else if (nPins < 50)
2190  w *= 1.6;
2191  else if (nPins < 100)
2192  w *= 1.8;
2193  else if (nPins < 200)
2194  w *= 2.1;
2195  else
2196  w *= 2.5;
2197 
2198  float tmp_rightX = getRightPinX(), tmp_bottomY = getBottomPinY(), tmp_leftX = getLeftPinX(),
2199  tmp_topY = getTopPinY();
2200 
2201  int A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX;
2202  placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_rightX, tmp_bottomY, A_ClockRegionX,
2203  A_ClockRegionY);
2204  std::pair<int, int> A_ClockLocYX(A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX);
2205 
2206  int B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX;
2207  placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_leftX, tmp_topY, B_cellClockRegionX,
2208  B_cellClockRegionY);
2209  std::pair<int, int> B_ClockLocYX(B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX);
2210 
2211  float clockRegionW = 0;
2212 
2213  w *= designNet->getOverallEnhanceRatio();
2214  if (updateX)
2215  {
2216  if (checkClockRegion && B_cellClockRegionX != A_ClockRegionX)
2217  {
2218  clockRegionW = 1 + std::abs(B_cellClockRegionX - A_ClockRegionX) * 32 /
2219  (float)(pinOffsetsInUnit.size() - 1) * 0.01;
2220  if (clockRegionW > 3)
2221  clockRegionW = 3;
2222  // w *= clockRegionW;
2223  }
2224 
2225  // add net between left node and right node
2226  addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, leftPuId, rightPuId,
2227  leftPUX, rightPUX, pinOffsetsInUnit[leftPinId_net].x, pinOffsetsInUnit[rightPinId_net].x,
2228  !unitsOfNetPins[leftPinId_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[rightPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2229  designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(leftPinId_net, rightPinId_net) * w /
2230  std::max(minDist, rightPinX - leftPinX));
2231 
2232  // add net between internal node and left/right node
2233  for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2234  {
2235  auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2236  auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2237  auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2238  float curX = tmpPU->X();
2239  bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
2240  if (pinId_net != leftPinId_net && pinId_net != rightPinId_net)
2241  {
2242  addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, leftPuId,
2243  curX, leftPUX, tmpPinOffset.x, pinOffsetsInUnit[leftPinId_net].x, movable,
2244  !unitsOfNetPins[leftPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2245  designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, leftPinId_net) * w /
2246  std::max(minDist, (curX + tmpPinOffset.x) - leftPinX));
2247  addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, rightPuId,
2248  curX, rightPUX, tmpPinOffset.x, pinOffsetsInUnit[rightPinId_net].x, movable,
2249  !unitsOfNetPins[rightPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2250  designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, rightPinId_net) * w /
2251  std::max(minDist, rightPinX - (curX + tmpPinOffset.x)));
2252  }
2253  }
2254  }
2255  if (updateY)
2256  {
2257 
2258  w *= y2xRatio;
2259 
2260  // add net between top node and bottom node
2261  addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, bottomPuId, topPuId,
2262  bottomPUY, topPUY, pinOffsetsInUnit[bottomPinId_net].y, pinOffsetsInUnit[topPinId_net].y,
2263  !unitsOfNetPins[bottomPinId_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[topPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2264  designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(topPinId_net, bottomPinId_net) * w /
2265  std::max(minDist, topPinY - bottomPinY));
2266 
2267  // add net between internal node and top/bottom node
2268  for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2269  {
2270  auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2271  auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2272  auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2273  float curY = tmpPU->Y();
2274  bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
2275  if (pinId_net != topPinId_net && pinId_net != bottomPinId_net)
2276  {
2277  addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, bottomPuId,
2278  curY, bottomPUY, tmpPinOffset.y, pinOffsetsInUnit[bottomPinId_net].y, movable,
2279  !unitsOfNetPins[bottomPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2280  designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, bottomPinId_net) * w /
2281  std::max(minDist, (curY + tmpPinOffset.y) - bottomPinY));
2282  addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, topPuId,
2283  curY, topPUY, tmpPinOffset.y, pinOffsetsInUnit[topPinId_net].y, movable,
2284  !unitsOfNetPins[topPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2285  designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, topPinId_net) * w /
2286  std::max(minDist, topPinY - (curY + tmpPinOffset.y)));
2287  }
2288  }
2289  }
2290  }

2292  inline void addPseudoNet_enhancePin2Pin(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2293  std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag,
2294  Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, float generalWeight, float y2xRatio,
2295  bool updateX, bool updateY, int PUIdA, int PUIdB, int pinIdA_net,
2296  int pinIdB_net)
2297  {
2298  float w = generalWeight;
2299 
2300  if (updateX)
2301  {
2302  // add net between left node and right node
2303  addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, PUIdA, PUIdB,
2304  unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->X(), unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->X(),
2305  pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdA_net].x, pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdB_net].x,

2307  }

2310  w *= y2xRatio;
2311 
2312  // add net between top node and bottom node

2314  unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->Y(), unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->Y(),
2315  pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdA_net].y, pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdB_net].y,
2316  !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->isFixed(), w);
2317  }

2342  inline void addB2BNet(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2343  std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag, Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, int puId0,
2344  int puId1, float pos0, float pos1, float pinOffset0, float pinOffset1, bool movable0,
2345  bool movable1, float w)
2346  {
2347  // min_x 0.5 * x'Px + q'x
2348  // s.t. l <= Ax <= u
2349  if (puId0 == puId1)
2350  return;
2351  if (movable0 && movable1)
2352  {
2353  // x0^2 + x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2354  // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
2355  // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
2356  objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
2357  objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
2358  objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId1, -w));
2359  objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId0, -w));
2360  if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2361  {
2362  // 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2363  objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
2364  objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
2365  }
2366  }
2367  else if (movable0)
2368  {
2369  // x0^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0
2370  // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
2371  objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
2372  objectiveVector[puId0] += -w * pos1;
2373  if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2374  {
2375  // 2(x0c-x1c)x0
2376  objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
2377  }
2378  }
2379  else if (movable1)
2380  {
2381  // x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2382  // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
2383  objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
2384  objectiveVector[puId1] += -w * pos0;
2385  if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2386  {
2387  // 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2388  objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
2389  }
2390  }
2391  }

2997  inline std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> *
2998  findNeiborLUTFFsFromBinGrid(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell, float displacementUpperbound, int minNumNeighbor = 10)
2999  {
3000  // please note that the input DesignCell is only used to find the corresponding binGrid for site search.
3001  bool findLUT = curCell->isLUT();
3002  float targetX = cellId2location[curCell->getCellId()].X;
3003  float targetY = cellId2location[curCell->getCellId()].Y;
3004  std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> *res = new std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *>();
3005  res->clear();
3006 
3007  int binIdX, binIdY;
3008  getGridXY(targetX, targetY, binIdX, binIdY);
3009 
3010  assert(binIdY >= 0);
3011  assert((unsigned int)binIdY < LUTFFBinGrid.size());
3012  assert(binIdX >= 0);
3013  assert((unsigned int)binIdX < LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY].size());
3014  assert(LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY][binIdX]->inRange(targetX, targetY));
3015 
3016  std::queue<std::pair<int, int>> binXYqueue;
3017  std::set<std::pair<int, int>> reachedBinXYs;
3018  binXYqueue.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3019  reachedBinXYs.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3020 
3021  bool findItself = false;
3022 
3023  while (binXYqueue.size() > 0)
3024  {
3025  std::pair<int, int> curXY = binXYqueue.front();
3026  binXYqueue.pop();
3027  int curbinIdX = curXY.first, curbinIdY = curXY.second;
3028 
3029  PlacementInfo::PlacementBinInfo *curBin = LUTFFBinGrid[curbinIdY][curbinIdX];
3030  float bin2TargetXYDistance = curBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3031  if (bin2TargetXYDistance > displacementUpperbound)
3032  continue;
3033  for (auto tmpCell : curBin->getCells())
3034  {
3035  if ((tmpCell->isLUT() && findLUT) || (tmpCell->isFF() && !findLUT))
3036  {
3037  float tmpX = cellId2location[tmpCell->getCellId()].X;
3038  float tmpY = cellId2location[tmpCell->getCellId()].Y;
3039  float tmpPUDis = fabs(targetX - tmpX) + y2xRatio * fabs(targetY - tmpY);
3040  if (tmpPUDis <= displacementUpperbound)
3041  {
3042  if (tmpCell == curCell)
3043  {
3044  findItself = true;
3045  }
3046  res->push_back(tmpCell);
3047  }
3048  }
3049  }
3050  assert(findItself);
3051  for (int nextY = curbinIdY - 1; nextY <= curbinIdY + 1; nextY++)
3052  {
3053  for (int nextX = curbinIdX - 1; nextX <= curbinIdX + 1; nextX++)
3054  {
3055  if (!(nextY >= 0))
3056  continue;
3057  if (!((unsigned int)nextY < LUTFFBinGrid.size()))
3058  continue;
3059  if (!(nextX >= 0))
3060  continue;
3061  if (!((unsigned int)nextX < LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY].size()))
3062  continue;
3063  PlacementInfo::PlacementBinInfo *nextBin = LUTFFBinGrid[nextY][nextX];
3064  float nextBin2TargetXYDistance = nextBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3065  if (nextBin2TargetXYDistance > displacementUpperbound)
3066  continue;
3067  std::pair<int, int> nextXY(nextX, nextY);
3068  if (reachedBinXYs.find(nextXY) == reachedBinXYs.end())
3069  {
3070  reachedBinXYs.insert(nextXY);
3071  binXYqueue.push(nextXY);
3072  }
3073  }
3074  }
3075  }
3076 
3077  assert(findItself);
3078  return res;
3079  }

3148  inline void addB2BNetInPlacementInfo(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
3149  std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag, Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector,
3150  int puId0, int puId1, float pos0, float pos1, float pinOffset0,
3151  float pinOffset1, bool movable0, bool movable1, float w)
3152  {
3153  // min_x 0.5 * x'Px + q'x
3154  // s.t. l <= Ax <= u
3155  if (puId0 == puId1)
3156  return;
3157  if (movable0 && movable1)
3158  {
3159  // x0^2 + x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3160  // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
3161  // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
3162  objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
3163  objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
3164  objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId1, -w));
3165  objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId0, -w));
3166  if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
3167  {
3168  // 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3169  objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
3170  objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
3171  }
3172  }
3173  else if (movable0)
3174  {
3175  // x0^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0
3176  // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
3177  objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
3178  objectiveVector[puId0] += -w * pos1;
3179  if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
3180  {
3181  // 2(x0c-x1c)x0
3182  objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
3183  }
3184  }
3185  else if (movable1)
3186  {
3187  // x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3188  // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
3189  objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
3190  objectiveVector[puId1] += -w * pos0;
3191  if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
3192  {
3193  // 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3194  objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
3195  }
3196  }
3197  }

3787  inline std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *> *
3788  findNeiborSiteFromBinGrid(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell, float targetX, float targetY,
3789  float displacementThreshold, int siteNumThreshold, bool checkClockRegion = false)
3790  {
3791  // please note that the input DesignCell is only used to find the corresponding binGrid for site search.
3792  std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *> *res = new std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *>(0);
3793 
3794  int binIdX, binIdY;
3795  getGridXY(targetX, targetY, binIdX, binIdY);
3796  auto curPU = getPlacementUnitByCellId(curCell->getCellId());
3797  int targetClockRegionX = -1;
3798  if (PU2ClockRegionColumn.find(curPU) != PU2ClockRegionColumn.end() && checkClockRegion)
3799  {
3800  targetClockRegionX = PU2ClockRegionColumn[curPU];
3801  }
3802 
3803  while (res->size() == 0)
3804  {
3805  auto sharedTypeIds = getPotentialBELTypeIDs(curCell->getCellType());
3806 
3807  for (auto sharedTypeId : sharedTypeIds)
3808  {
3809  assert((unsigned int)curCell->getCellId() < cellId2CellBinInfo.size());
3810  assert(binIdY >= 0);
3811  assert((unsigned int)binIdY < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId].size());
3812  assert(binIdX >= 0);
3813  assert((unsigned int)binIdX < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId][binIdY].size());
3814 
3815  std::vector<std::vector<PlacementBinInfo *>> &curBinGrid = SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId];
3816 
3817  std::queue<std::pair<int, int>> binXYqueue;
3818  std::set<std::pair<int, int>> reachedBinXYs;
3819  binXYqueue.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3820  reachedBinXYs.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3821 
3822  while (binXYqueue.size() > 0)
3823  {
3824  std::pair<int, int> curXY = binXYqueue.front();
3825  binXYqueue.pop();
3826  int curbinIdX = curXY.first, curbinIdY = curXY.second;
3827 
3828  PlacementBinInfo *curBin = curBinGrid[curbinIdY][curbinIdX];
3829  float bin2TargetXYDistance = curBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3830  if (bin2TargetXYDistance > displacementThreshold)
3831  continue;
3832  int findSiteCnt = 0;
3833  for (auto curSite : curBin->getCorrespondingSites())
3834  {
3835  if (!curSite->isOccupied() && !curSite->isMapped())
3836  {
3837  if (getDisplacement(targetX, targetY, curSite) < displacementThreshold)
3838  {
3839  findSiteCnt++;
3840  if (targetClockRegionX >= 0 && targetClockRegionX != curSite->getClockRegionX())
3841  continue;
3842  res->push_back(curSite);
3843  }
3844  }
3845  }
3846 
3847  if (res->size() < (unsigned int)siteNumThreshold)
3848  {
3849  for (int nextY = curbinIdY - 1; nextY <= curbinIdY + 1; nextY++)
3850  {
3851  for (int nextX = curbinIdX - 1; nextX <= curbinIdX + 1; nextX++)
3852  {
3853  if (!(nextY >= 0))
3854  continue;
3855  if (!((unsigned int)nextY < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId].size()))
3856  continue;
3857  if (!(nextX >= 0))
3858  continue;
3859  if (!((unsigned int)nextX < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId][binIdY].size()))
3860  continue;
3861  PlacementBinInfo *nextBin = curBinGrid[nextY][nextX];
3862  float nextBin2TargetXYDistance = nextBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3863  if (nextBin2TargetXYDistance > displacementThreshold)
3864  continue;
3865  std::pair<int, int> nextXY(nextX, nextY);
3866  if (reachedBinXYs.find(nextXY) == reachedBinXYs.end())
3867  {
3868  reachedBinXYs.insert(nextXY);
3869  binXYqueue.push(nextXY);
3870  }
3871  }
3872  }
3873  }
3874  }
3875  }
3876  displacementThreshold *= 1.5;
3877  }
3878 
3879  return res;
3880  }

4116  inline unsigned int getPairPinNum(DesignInfo::DesignCell *LUTA, DesignInfo::DesignCell *LUTB)
4117  {
4118  if (LUTA->getInputPins().size() == 6 || LUTB->getInputPins().size() == 6 || LUTA->isLUT6() || LUTB->isLUT6())
4119  return 12;
4120 
4121  int pinNumA = 0;
4122  int totalPin = 0;
4123  int netIds[5]; // be aware that a LUT might have pins connected to the same net and they should be treated as
4124  // different inputs.
4125 
4126  for (auto tmpPin : LUTA->getInputPins())
4127  {
4128  if (!tmpPin->isUnconnected())
4129  {
4130  netIds[pinNumA] = tmpPin->getNet()->getElementIdInType();
4131  pinNumA++;
4132  }
4133  }
4134  totalPin = pinNumA;
4135  for (auto tmpPin : LUTB->getInputPins())
4136  {
4137  if (!tmpPin->isUnconnected())
4138  {
4139  bool matched = false;
4140  for (int i = 0; i < pinNumA; i++)
4141  {
4142  if (netIds[i] >= 0 && netIds[i] == tmpPin->getNet()->getElementIdInType())
4143  {
4144  netIds[i] = -1;
4145  matched = true;
4146  break;
4147  }
4148  }
4149  if (!matched)
4150  {
4151  totalPin++;
4152  }
4153  }
4154  }
4155  return totalPin;
4156  }
